  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="sonnet">
        <lg type="1st quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Just like the waves washing stones to the shore</l>
            <l>our time is limited.</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>With every place it is being washed to</l>
            <l>it <choice><orig>enavitably</orig><reg>inevitably</reg></choice> all comes to an end.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="2nd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>A baby after being born</l>
            <l>matures to the height of his life</l>
            <l>as time begins to strike</l>
            <l>what once was a gift now causes death</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="3rd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Beauty fades with time</l>
            <l>And marks beauty's brow</l>
            <l>Nourished by nature</l>
            <l>And nothing is certain except for death.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="final couplet">
          <s>
            <l>I hope my poem lasts the test of time,</l>
            <l>Praising your worth even after we have passed.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
